# =========================================================================
# GMAIL SMTP & PORTFOLIO CONTACT FORM CONFIGURATION EXAMPLE
# =========================================================================
#
# INSTRUCTIONS:
# 1. Copy this file and rename it to ".env.local" in the root directory.
# 2. Fill in the values below with your personal Gmail configuration.
# 3. DO NOT commit ".env.local" to git (it is ignored by default to keep secrets safe).
#

# -------------------------------------------------------------------------
# 1. GMAIL_USER (Your Gmail Address)
# -------------------------------------------------------------------------
# The email address that will be used to authenticate with Gmail SMTP.
# Example: GMAIL_USER=yourname.ece24@bitsindri.ac.in or yourname@gmail.com
GMAIL_USER=mdkaif.ece24@bitsindri.ac.in

# -------------------------------------------------------------------------
# 2. GMAIL_APP_PASSWORD (16-Character Google App Password)
# -------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Crucial: Gmail does NOT allow you to use your regular Gmail password here.
# You MUST generate an "App Password" by following these simple steps:
#
#   Step A: Go to your Google Account Settings (https://myaccount.google.com/)
#   Step B: Click on the "Security" tab in the left-hand menu.
#   Step C: Under "How you sign in to Google", make sure "2-Step Verification" is turned ON.
#   Step D: Click on "2-Step Verification" and scroll down to the bottom.
#   Step E: Click on "App passwords".
#   Step F: Enter an App Name (e.g. "Portfolio Website") and click "Create".
#   Step G: Copy the 16-character code shown (e.g. "abcd efgh ijkl mnop").
#   Step H: Paste it below WITHOUT spaces (e.g. "abcdefghijklmnop").
#
GMAIL_APP_PASSWORD=abcdefghijklmnop

# -------------------------------------------------------------------------
# 3. CONTACT_RECEIVER_EMAIL (Optional Destination Email)
# -------------------------------------------------------------------------
# The email address where you want to receive the portfolio messages.
# If left blank, it will automatically fall back and send to your GMAIL_USER.
# Example: CONTACT_RECEIVER_EMAIL=recipient@gmail.com

# Web3Forms - FREE contact form relay for static sites (GitHub Pages)
# Get your key at: https://web3forms.com -> Enter email -> Get key instantly
NEXT_PUBLIC_WEB3FORMS_KEY=your_web3forms_access_key_here
CONTACT_RECEIVER_EMAIL=mdkaif.ece24@bitsindri.ac.in
